{"tid":1154243,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"金庸武林門派地圖：六大派圍攻光明頂＝西天取經？","createTime":"2019-05-14T06:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T07:03:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"87cfc96b3fb2b229e7b5cdd5d7c9dbc3e81e7397","tid":1154243,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T06:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/11/05/99/5491132.jpg&amp;s=Y&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=690&amp;sh=561&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F11%2F05%2F99%2F5491132.jpg%26s%3DY%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D690%26sh%3D561%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&h=e7453086&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源／微博<br />\n<br />\n「萬萬沒想到神龍教開口是東北話」<br />\n<br />\n「古墓派居然在陝西，那麼－－『過兒，餓錯咧，餓真滴錯咧，餓從一開始就不應該出墓&hellip;』」<br />\n<br />\n「說真的，謝遜為了報復成昆也是拼了，殺個人走3年啊」<br />\n<br />\n「紅花會這麼遠要怎麼反清復明啊」<br />\n<br />\n「五嶽根本距離超遠，一次公文傳輸要跑遍全國啊，左冷禪你是拿到空間寶石，還是炫耀輕功」<br />\n<br />\n「光明頂真的太遠了，混江湖太難，這個武林盟主我不當了」<br />\n<br />\n六大派是多想不開啊，一路遠征巴基斯坦邊境！<br />\n<br />\n難怪白眉鷹王去個武當派要騎死八匹馬，再堅持一下就是六大派西天取經了好嗎！！<br />\n<br />\n「不是&hellip;這光明頂攻下來是要幹嘛用&hellip;&hellip;」<br />\n<br />\n「決戰光明頂估計離得遠的門派從出生就出發了，邊走邊修練」<br />\n<br />\n「光明頂這麼遠，中原高手可能去了有高原反應」<br />\n<br />\n「光明頂&hellip;&hellip;走著走著都tm迷路了」<br />\n<br />\n「六大派是不是閒的蛋疼？跨越半個中國去遭一頓毒打」<br />\n<br />\n「表面上是圍攻光明頂，實際上是支持一帶一路政策」<br />\n<br />\n事實上，張無忌出生的冰火島才叫遠。據書中描述，張翠山、殷素素、謝遜從江浙一帶出發向東後，遭遇風暴導致船損只能順著洋流漂行，後來再換浮冰繼續北漂才上島，該處晝長夜短，位置近北極，卻有活火山。據傳就是阿拉斯加西部的阿留申群島，張教主根本一出生就領綠卡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/11/05/99/5491173.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F11%2F05%2F99%2F5491173.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&h=c3731638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源／新浪看點<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://oops.udn.com/oops/story/6699/3462144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foops.udn.com%2Foops%2Fstory%2F6699%2F3462144&d=%2Bo3sOR8bLgAbrAMBqI8fZy1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=89c7f37f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://oops.udn.com/oops/story/6699/3462144</a>"},{"pid":"ff15354bfbd1ff89d43bebbf95203653d5185eaa","tid":1154243,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:03:07.000Z","msg":"其實就咁睇同當年金庸群俠傳online地圖差不多<br />\n地理好相近"},{"pid":"3f467faf0c5ac9b12a004048c25d0c0946b86f3d","tid":1154243,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:04:19.000Z","msg":"原來桃花島係上海"},{"pid":"05047ffd4f344591d26d973ece40d8ebe8fcf919","tid":1154243,"uid":94828,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:08:05.000Z","msg":"在虛構的故事當中尋求真實感的人腦袋一定有問題"},{"pid":"181d6f38db60cebdf678c2d55f4ddc4695d79d1c","tid":1154243,"uid":435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:48:27.000Z","msg":"原來張無忌係美國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3332f13f5fa55baad9ed281cf91f63597ce69abf","tid":1154243,"uid":1255,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"181d6f38db60cebdf678c2d55f4ddc4695d79d1c","tid":1154243,"uid":435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:48:27.000Z","msg":"原來張無忌係美國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:51:29.000Z","msg":"唔怪得溝死女啦<br />\n原來係洋腸黎"},{"pid":"f8552dda2fdfa3e4a1d1d65db8c1350edcdcfc89","tid":1154243,"uid":137217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"181d6f38db60cebdf678c2d55f4ddc4695d79d1c","tid":1154243,"uid":435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07:48:27.000Z","msg":"原來張無忌係美國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T07: